headline: Camden Property Trust Announces Fourth Quarter 2024 Dividend
summary: HOUSTON, December 04, 2024--The Board of Trust Managers of Camden Property Trust (NYSE:CPT) (the "Company") declared a fourth quarter cash dividend of $1.03 per share to holders of record as of December 18, 2024 of its Common Shares of Beneficial Interest. The dividend is to be paid on January 17, 2025.
